    <p class="small">Most Wood Stone calls land $400–$800 parts-and-labor. Refractory major refurbish and flame-impingement specialty work run higher. See our <a href="/price-list/commercial-oven-repair-cost/">commercial oven repair cost guide</a>.</p>
